SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT ppr_id, r1.reference_date, re.re_nummer, re.re_rekening, re.re_soort, greatest(re.re_openingsdatum, ~3) "START_EXPOSURE", least(to_date(~4,'YYYYMMDD') ,nvl(t.tnst_date,to_date ('31-12-9999','DD-MM-YYYY')) ) "END_EXPOSURE" FROM producten_per_relatie pr INNER JOIN rekeningen_per_product rp ON rp.rpp_productnummer = pr.ppr_productnummer AND rp.rpp_volgnr_per_product = pr.ppr_volgnr_per_product AND rp.rpp_relatienummer = pr.ppr_relatienummer AND rp.rpp_rekeningsoort BETWEEN 100 AND 999 AND rp.rpp_valuta = ' ' INNER JOIN rekeningen re ON re.re_nummer = pr.ppr_relatienummer AND re.re_rekening = rp.rpp_rekening_nummer AND re.re_soort = rp.rpp_rekeningsoort AND re.re_muntsoort = rp.rpp_valuta LEFT OUTER JOIN TOSA_ACCOUNT_TERMINATION t on t.tnhd_ppr_id = pr.ppr_id, tosa_reference_dates_taxyear r1 WHERE pr.ppr_id = ~1 AND ( t.tnst_date is null OR ( t.tnst_date >= to_date(~3,'YYYYMMDD') AND r1.reference_date < t.tnst_date ) ) AND re.re_openingsdatum <= ~4 AND r1.reference_date >= to_date(re.re_openingsdatum, 'YYYYMMDD') AND r1.tax_year = ~2 AND r1.reference_date <= to_date(~4,'YYYYMMDD')
ORDER BY 1, 2

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT instrument_id, position, v.quote "INSTRUMENT_QUOTE", b.be_muntsoort, b.be_prijs_factor, v2.quote "CURRENCY_QUOTE" FROM ( SELECT FIRST_VALUE(id) OVER(PARTITION BY instrument_id ORDER BY position_date DESC ) first, id, instrument_id, position_date, position FROM nominative_register WHERE ppr_id = ~1 AND position_date <= to_date(~2, 'YYYYMMDD') ) inner join beleggingsinstrument b on b.be_volgnummer=instrument_id --Only TOSA applicable records: AND b.be_tsa_ind=1 inner join beleggingsinstrument b2 on b2.be_symbool=b.be_muntsoort and b2.be_optietype=' ' and b2.be_expiratiedatum = '00000000' and b2.be_exerciseprijs=0 left outer join pc_quote_per_day_vw v on v.be_id=instrument_id and v.quote_date=to_date(~2, 'YYYYMMDD') left outer join pc_quote_per_day_vw v2 on v2.be_id=b2.be_volgnummer and v2.quote_date=to_date(~2, 'YYYYMMDD') WHERE id = first

SQL_STMT_U.val: -- Blocked positions and quotes on or before a given reference date: SELECT b.be_volgnummer, p.bpos_aantal_nominaal, v.quote "INSTRUMENT_QUOTE", b.be_muntsoort, b.be_prijs_factor, v2.quote "CURRENCY_QUOTE" FROM geblokkeerde_positie p INNER JOIN beleggingsinstrument b ON b.be_symbool = p.bpos_fondssymbool AND b.be_optietype = ' ' AND b.be_expiratiedatum = '00000000' AND b.be_exerciseprijs = 0 --Only TOSA applicable records: AND b.be_tsa_ind=1 INNER JOIN beleggingsinstrument b2 ON b2.be_symbool = b.be_muntsoort AND b2.be_optietype = ' ' AND b2.be_expiratiedatum = '00000000' AND b2.be_exerciseprijs = 0 LEFT OUTER JOIN pc_quote_per_day_vw v ON v.be_id = b.be_volgnummer AND v.quote_date = to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') LEFT OUTER JOIN pc_quote_per_day_vw v2 ON v2.be_id = b2.be_volgnummer AND v2.quote_date = to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') WHERE p.bpos_categorie = ~2 AND p.bpos_blokkeringsrt = ~3 AND p.bpos_relatienr = ~4 AND p.bpos_rekeningnr = ~5 AND p.bpos_rekeningsoort = ~6 AND p.bpos_rekeningmuntsr = ' ' AND p.bpos_ingangsdatum <= ~1 AND ( p.bpos_vervaldatum = '00000000' OR p.bpos_vervaldatum >= ~1)
